==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Punt-out
<hw>Punt"-out`</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(American Football)</fld> <def>A
punt made from the goal line by a player of the side which has made a
touchdown to one of his own side for a fair catch, from which an attempt
to kick a goal may be made.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Punty</ent>⟦br⟧
